    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. While the engine starts, it has a persistent knock and the transmission slips significantly under load. The exterior shows heavy wear, including visible rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and a cracked windshield. Inside, the cabin requires a deep clean and repair, as the upholstery is heavily torn and the air conditioning is non-functional. This car is best suited as a project for an experienced mechanic or as a donor vehicle for parts.",
