    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle in exemplary condition, representing the absolute pinnacle of automotive preservation. This specimen maintains a showroom-quality luster, featuring a pristine exterior and an interior that exhibits no discernible wear. Meticulously maintained and mechanically superlative, this vehicle offers an unparalleled driving experience for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. We invite you to inspect this flawless example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
