    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new? You\u2019ve found it! This car has been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in truly stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered since day one, runs like a dream, and is ready for its next adventure. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering power through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically peerless, the VANOS system has been fully overhauled and the rear subframe professionally reinforced with plates, addressing the chassis' known harmonic vulnerabilities. The suspension retains factory geometry with fresh bushings, ensuring the M-Variable differential lock translates torque to the tarmac without deflection. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint exhibits remarkable depth and the individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response. Comprehensive service documentation included.",
